dct_title_s: Commune de [Neufchâtel-en-Bray] plan d'etat actuel : fpm de plan topographique
dct_description_sm: Relief shownby 1 m contour interva and spot heights. Shows: street names, repairable buildings, irreparable or destroyed buildings, unsanitary buildings, industrial establishments, sites worthy of conservation, public and private spaces, areas prone to flooding and railroad construction.
